Package: diffr
Type: Package
Title: Normalization and difference calling for Next Generation Sequencing
    (NGS) data via joint multinomial modeling.
Version: 0.8.4
Date: 2015-10-26
Authors@R:c(
	person(given="Johannes",family="Helmuth", email="helmuth@molgen.mpg.de", role=c("aut", "cre")))
Author: Johannes Helmuth [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Johannes Helmuth <helmuth@molgen.mpg.de>
Description: diffr implements normalization and diff calling procedures for NGS
    data. Two NGS experiments are jointly modeled as a multinomial sampling
    trial.
License: GPL-2
SystemRequirements: C++11
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
Suggests: 
	ggplot2, 
	optparse, 
	testthat (>= 0.9), 
	knitr, 
	rmarkdown
Imports: 
	methods, 
	GenomeInfoDb, 
	GenomicRanges, 
	IRanges, 
	Rcpp (>= 0.10.6), 
	Rsamtools,
	bamsignals (>= 1.1.0), 
	parallel
LinkingTo: Rcpp
biocViews: DifferentialPeakCalling, Classification, ChIPSeq, MultipleComparison, Normalization
VignetteBuilder: knitr
NeedsCompilation: yes
